For the 2004/2005 marketing year:
(a) the minimum price referred to in Article 3 of Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 for dried ‘d'Ente’ plums shall be EUR 1 935,23 per tonne net ex-producer's premises;
(b) the production aid referred to in Article 4 of that Regulation for prunes shall be EUR 923,17 per tonne net.
